# Protect local homelab secrets

See `beelink-cleanup/.cursor/rules/protect-local-secrets.mdc` for the full policy.

Agents must **never** delete, move, overwrite, or commit private keys (`homelab`, `beelink`, `blackpearl`), `.env`, or kubeconfig files.

If keys are missing on the Windows client, instruct the user to restore from blackpearl or Mac — do not rotate cluster keys without explicit approval.
